{"tid":1303931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[白色恐怖round 2]而家呢個形勢應該要煲大TVB 廣告霸權黎回應聲明","createTime":"2019-07-10T12:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T13:16:18.000Z","uid":38548,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"566a1b528e494bd6c7d1468a7b9b9f082ca68009","tid":1303931,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:54:09.000Z","msg":"TVB 段聲明絕對係誤導緊市民<br />\n唔落佢地廣告 = 支持暴力<br />\n完全唔合乎邏輯<br />\n<br />\n而家市民因為各種原因愈黎愈少睇TVB <br />\n政治立場係其中一大因素 人地抽起廣告都係商業決定<br />\n係唔係有示威個陣所有商家都唔俾抽起廣告？<br />\n<br />\n明顯佢地目的係要嚇疾其他想抽廣告既商家<br />\n用大陸市場 政治立場綁架 黎維持自己利益<br />\n<br />\n仆街程度唔會低過班獅子狗<br />\n係另類白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n連登仔要諗諗對策"},{"pid":"95c1ca316f520cbca68b4d63051fe640fe5c651e","tid":1303931,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:54:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8379f7fc0a0710357239bce9820773bbf11fe81a","tid":1303931,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:55:07.000Z","msg":"歡迎大家有咩講可以講晒佢"},{"pid":"a373876f26dde7491e85562267fb073cb6c27d01","tid":1303931,"uid":265902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:55:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3354e6607359ca3e9d4f26cfa2e27949014640fb","tid":1303931,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:57:00.000Z","msg":"白色恐怖無處不在<br />\n<br />\n仲掛住睇愛回家？"},{"pid":"c8a0a2535b83b66f5bcd0b01445c4fd86f094d65","tid":1303931,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:57:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<br />\n今次好唔尋常<br />\n<br />\nTVB先向國家宣傳機器環球時報獨家披露回應<br />\n<br />\n之後由文匯率先報導<br />\n<br />\n再逼到POCARI跪低<br />\n<br />\n之後出一個得罪香港AT LEAST 200萬人嘅聲明<br />\n<br />\n非常值得大家深思<br />\n係咪直接由中聯辦控制緊TVB</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9b722682a89ebf0c5b003f50dab2385e0e40c2dc","tid":1303931,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:57: